*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
function cdxmdst(cyytmdst,ctagname)
index on           MEDIDNO      tag (ctagname+"1") of (cyytmdst) option indexbar()
index on MEDLSTNAM+MEDFSTNAM    tag (ctagname+"2") of (cyytmdst) option indexbar()
